<section class="vc-feat" style="padding-top:0; padding-bottom:80px;">
  <div class="vc-feat-rubric reveal">What your gift funds</div>
  <h2 class="vc-feat-h reveal">Every tier is a <em>named act.</em></h2>
  <article class="vc-prose reveal" style="max-width:780px; margin:0 auto;">

<p class="drop"><strong>$25 — Sustain.</strong> One month of research database access for the BDI Sovereign Dataset. The record stays open because it is funded. Your $25 keeps one data pipeline lit.</p>

<p><strong>$50 — Build.</strong> One week of curriculum development materials for McCartney Academy's founding cohort. The school is being built now. Every piece of material is funded here, before a single student enrolls, because that is when it matters.</p>

<p><strong>$100 — Anchor.</strong> One month of operational infrastructure for a FarmBlock cooperative pilot site — soil testing, tool maintenance, cooperative meeting space. Phase I is live in 2026. These dollars are what Phase I runs on.</p>

<p><strong>$250 — Steward.</strong> A full quarterly data verification cycle for one BDI Dataset pillar. The record is only sovereign if the data is accurate. Stewards fund the verification pass that makes it defensible in court, in Congress, and in the community that depends on it.</p>

<p><strong>$500 — Transform.</strong> One full scholarship unit toward the Block to the Boardroom leadership pipeline — covering materials, civic access events, and mentorship programming for one participant moving from neighborhood organizing to policy authorship.</p>

<p><strong>$1,000 — Patron.</strong> A named Patron contribution to the McCartney Academy Founding Fund. Patron-level gifts are tracked publicly. The founding generation of the Academy is the people who funded it before it existed. That record is permanent.</p>

  </article>
</section>

<section class="vc-feat" style="background:var(--vc-bone); padding:64px 0;">
